e":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T14:00:52.000Z","msg":"我個度其他intern都好好人 雖然去到最後開始有小圈子<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上頭都比幾多野做 不過間接令到自己學到好多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人工又高 Last Day個日心情好沉重<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b0c5161ed145ad537a5c1294cbdf30510e8d59e","tid":788490,"uid":11862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T14:12:31.000Z","msg":"會<br />\n啲同事都幾啱傾<br />\n但份工好撚悶 唔想返去做 人工又低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b8fca5f74614c6b401ed9ae1bcacd57aa2f5fad","tid":788490,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T14:20:37.000Z","msg":"記得買散水餅"},{"pid":"61b806b4191c2b29fa8e60e704c4570b33ffb190","tid":788490,"uid":94465,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T15:38:27.000Z","msg":"覺得好對唔住上司同事<br />\n好想快啲走<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84898a03096e16bb674ae10ee3e0c95d07f10477","tid":788490,"uid":12731,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T15:44:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我唔係intern，但我睇住啲intern<br />\n<br />\n我好唔捨得啲intern bb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我都係果度intern出身，當年過得好開心，學左好多野，依家另一個身分返番嚟，好想比返呢啲野佢。話咁快佢都就走了，重返校園生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知佢又有無係度得到少少野，intern呢幾個月過得開唔開心呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e94a5f008037399764a35ccd5a04a96a91e1a69","tid":788490,"uid":25952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T15:53:46.000Z","msg":"對就完intern 無乜感覺<br />\n但完intern代表開學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a33ea6b4d67eddc991dc7c6ac7059afc7041b7b","tid":788490,"uid":124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T00:29:19.000Z","msg":"想快d完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79553425e8fae58db7ee383501d11f9b32f18cc7","tid":788490,"uid":48897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a33ea6b4d67eddc991dc7c6ac7059afc7041b7b","tid":788490,"uid":124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T00:29:19.000Z","msg":"想快d完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T00:36:02.000Z","msg":"同感<br />\n忙到嘔"},{"pid":"2e8743b0e6f8dee7a83ea6776f4004e76c50893f","tid":788490,"uid":110939,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T00:51:36.000Z","msg":"Ig 廣告呢啲 有啲客人只會睇followers數目多少，就比你做，通常過二千就有，明顯佢做開啲品牌唔出出名啦。<br />\n加上，廣告sale 既係商品，你個人柒啲，可能會focus位自然會落番係商品到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2691c43eb187718b41a51b000826dc6457e2ff3","tid":788490,"uid":73567,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T11:03:05.000Z","msg":"冇野學<br />\n日日重複性工作"},{"pid":"cf773976f72cda4396b9ddf90367a9c3e5af08f8","tid":788490,"uid":186845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T13:33:26.000Z","msg":"有"},{"pid":"192a071b975a6c115fe8882d95e66c2330d66731","tid":788490,"uid":125213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T14:02:20.000Z","msg":"忙到死 想早啲完<br />\n有日OT 9點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申:工程狗"},{"pid":"77984fa7a73b18a2aff1c1d911818ddb7a096d84","tid":788490,"uid":4120,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T15:09:05.000Z","msg":"無<br />\n想快啲完左佢<br />\n做得唔係太開心"},{"pid":"333fba2366d134fdb98a3478bd27105ef5c0456d","tid":788490,"uid":202198,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T15:51:37.